{"tid":554180,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"Quincy Jones: The Beatles係史上最差的樂隊","createTime":"2018-02-08T09:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T08:19:01.000Z","uid":119821,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fabd4eea68894e9dd0a4dbe2d40f24fb20549e54","tid":554180,"uid":119821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:10:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.vulture.com/2018/02/quincy-jones-in-conversation.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vulture.com%2F2018%2F02%2Fquincy-jones-in-conversation.html&d=%2FhX2HLq%2BMhUlGVxEIFXTI9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=489410a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vulture.com/2018/02/quincy-jones-in-conversation.html</a><br />\n<br />\n樂壇元老級人物一篇訪問，真心好睇<br />\n<br />\n重點:<br />\n<br />\n- Michael Jackson偷歌連10%都唔分比人，整容時期鳩吹自己有病先要整成咁，講到對MJ整容看法，表示因為年少時被父親家暴以及侮辱引致的。<br />\n<br />\n- Jimi Hendrix當年退出樂隊錄製係因為淆底(當年成員:Toots Thielemans, Herbie Hancock, Hubert Laws, Roland Kirk)<br />\n<br />\n- 對The Beatles: That they were the worst musicians in the world, Paul 玩Bass爛到仆街，Ringo搞首4 Bar搞成幾個鐘都唔掂<br />\n<br />\n- 問到U2到依家仲有冇做好音樂，搖頭回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 表示Bono壓力實在太大<br />\n<br />\n- Cyndi Lauper當年錄&quot;We Are the World&quot;慈善歌，屈鳩其他人&ldquo;The rockers don&rsquo;t like the song.&rdquo;比人罵到一面屁，罵完隨後錄歌&quot;fucking up every take&quot;因為身上的首飾太嘈入哂咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 批評現今音樂: It&rsquo;s just loops, beats, rhymes and hooks. What is there for me to learn from that? There ain&rsquo;t no fucking songs. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n- 覺得如今邊啲歌手好: Bruno Mars. Chance the Rapper. Kendrick Lamar, Ed Sheeran, Sam Smith, Mark Ronson<br />\n<br />\n- Marlon Brando 同James Baldwin. Richard Pryor. Marvin Gaye通通搞過哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多，不過大家慢慢睇，歡迎開火罵戰，不過只係一篇訪問，請大家勿認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4d757b45586f68155e5b21a232400ed9706a5e","tid":554180,"uid":10715,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:27:03.000Z","msg":"The Beatles技巧差就大家都知架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過hendrix淆底真係好好笑"},{"pid":"4e31377ca99e8c35cad05e60838f598e5389c814","tid":554180,"uid":95516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:27:26.000Z","msg":"其實Lou Reed都屌過Beatles垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1579b4ee50cdbe5ced08f822291118c406aae6f9","tid":554180,"uid":92360,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"- 覺得如今邊啲歌手好: Bruno Mars. Chance the Rapper. Kendrick Lamar, <span style=\"color: red;\">Ed Sheeran</span>, Sam Smith, Mark Ronson<br />\n<br />\n- Marlon Brando 同James Baldwin. Richard Pryor. Marvin Gaye通通搞過哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多，不過大家慢慢睇，歡迎開火罵戰，不過只係一篇訪問，請大家勿認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/no